# project_starter workflow rules

## Before starting any task

1. Run `python3 orchestrator.py` in the project root
2. Read `.ai/AI_CONTEXT.md` — ordered context for the current task
3. Read `.ai/WORKFLOW.md` — deterministic workflow plan

## Current workflow snapshot

{{WORKFLOW_CONTENT}}

## Post-task

Run all validators listed under "Post-task validators" in `.ai/WORKFLOW.md` in order before committing.

## Constraint

Document selection logic lives exclusively in `document-registry.yaml` and `orchestrator.py`. Do not add selection logic to adapter files.

## Regenerate

```bash
python3 orchestrator.py --adapter cursor
```
